verbose_text: In this study, 1,422 bp fragments from the GABRB3 gene 5 ' regulatory region were inserted into a pGL-3 luciferase reporter gene vector and transfected into HEK-293, SK-N-SH, and SH-SY5Y cells to examine the effects on luciferase protein expression by two haplotypes of T-G and C-A derived from NG_012836.1 : g.4160T> C and NG_012836.1 : g.4326G> A.
